title: Woman Standing Medium Skin Tone
description: A woman in a standing pose, depicted with a medium skin tone. It signifies a person, female identity, and a neutral or ready stance.

Her stance is upright and self-assured, with softly rounded edges contributing to her approachable yet dignified presence. This emoji is perfect for representing personal presence, action, or a statement of being in digital conversations.
